message.body: I'm going to the beach today! What are you up to?
Oh nice! What do you do for a living?
I used to work at a bookstore but I've been seeking other employment. Not having too much luck I'm afraid.
Ugh, I hear that frustration. I'm so sick of worrying about money. What would you like to do?
Honestly? Anything at this point. I'd love something involving a library to be honest. I'd love to go for a degree in criminal psychology.
Well I hope things work out for you soon. Applying for jobs is a (thankless) job on its own! So exhausting. What are you reading these days?
